this_title: The Secret of Skinwalker Ranch Season 1
trans_title: “皮行者牧场”的秘密 第一季
introduction: A team of scientists and experts who will conduct a thorough search in one of the most infamous and secretive hotspots of paranormal and UFO-related activities on earth,Skinwalker Ranch.They will attempt to find out the truth behind more than 200 years of mysteries - involving everything from UFO sightings and paranormal activities to animal mutilations and Native American legends of a shape-shifting creature known simply as as "The Skinwalker."一个由科学家和专家组成的团队将在地球上最臭名昭著和神秘的超自然和不明飞行物相关活动热点之一进行彻底的搜索，他们将试图找出200多年神秘事件背后的真相，从不明飞行物目击和超自然活动，到动物残肢和美洲原住民传说中的变形生物，简称为“剥皮行者”
